 <br>

  <li>Integrate the new AI assistance tools and methods into the operational processes of NED and the Exoplanet Archive, including folding in feedback from vetting by human experts to iteratively improve the AI-generated database load files.</li> 
  <li>Write, test, and edit documentation.</li> 
  <li>Participate in meetings (virtual and in-person).</li>

  <li>Experience and strong interest in machine learning methods.</li> 
  <li>Experience with programming in Python, R, or other scientific/technical computing language.</li> 
  <li>Good written and verbal communication skills, with an emphasis on the ability to share ideas in a collaborative and diverse setting.</li> 
 </ul>
